com.googlecode.prmf.merapi.net.irc
Class IrcCommands

java.lang.Object
  com.googlecode.prmf.merapi.net.irc.IrcCommands

public class IrcCommands
extends Object

Makes the sending of IRC commands less verbose.

I didn't want to pollute the IrcClient class with methods for every imaginable IRC action, but IrcClient.send(IrcCommand) is rather verbose. This is where this class (technically a library, because it's used procedurally) comes in. Try: 

 import static com.googlecode.lawu.net.irc.IrcCommands.*;
to get the IRC commands you've always wanted!

Author:
Miorel-Lucian Palii
See Also:
IrcClient
